for the thinking process of such a large entity would be the supra-conscious
thinking of the human race, but speeded up tremendously. By supra-conscious
thinking, I mean the collective thinking we do through such processes as evolving
languages, cultures, economies, science etc. Perhaps the subentities of a Jupiter
brain would have time for interesting and fulfilling social lives, and well as
contributing to the (to them) incomprehensible thinking of the collective entity.

