It's not faster than light but this phenomenon can transmit information,
teleportation can be used to get information out of a system without
causing quantum decoherence, that's why those who want to make a
quantum computer are interested in it.  Something like it has also been
used in real world in quantum cryptography to transfer financial information
between banks.

